  <Summary>Overview

Two great Goon stories for the price of one!

In the first story, the Goon and Franky make their way to the bottom of the sea in search of sunken treasure, only to fall into the clutches of a wretched, evil sea hag, who turns out to be lonely for a man.

In the second story, guest artist Kyle Hotz (The Agency, The Hood) joins Goon creator Eric Powell, as an insane skunk-ape ruins a pie-eating contest that the Goon has money riding on. Nothing comes between the Goon and his money!</Summary>
